## Architecture — Event-Driven Pattern

This MCP server reacts to events (webhooks, schedules, file changes). Tools
publish events; handlers subscribe and execute business logic asynchronously.
State is stored as **projections** (read models) — derived from the event log.

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    Tool[Tool Call] -->|publish| Bus[Event Bus]
    Bus -->|route| H1[Handler 1]
    Bus -->|route| H2[Handler 2]
    H1 -->|update| P[Projection Store]
    H2 -->|update| P
    P -->|read| Query[Query Tool]
```

